title: Indonesia : mobile phone internet users 2017 to 2023
yAxis: Number of mobile phone internet users in millions
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of mobile phone internet users in millions, containing a total of 7 data points.
Overall Number of mobile phone internet users in millions has increased over the Year.
Number of mobile phone internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2021, and finally roughly constant from 2021 to 2023.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Number of mobile phone internet users in millions, about 100.4 was reported at Year 2023
The lowest Number of mobile phone internet users in millions, of value 72.5 was reported at Year 2017
